OL,7,FA multi-million pound compensation
OL,8,Fclaim by owners evacuated from a
OL,9,FBelfast apartment block due to safety
OL,10,Fconcerns is to be dismissed, a High
OL,11,FCourt judge ruled today.
OL,13,FMr Justice Huddleston struck out the
OL,14,Fgroup action brought over structural
OL,15,Fissues at the Victoria Square
OL,16,Fresidential complex because a
OL,17,Flegislative time limit for mounting
OL,18,Fthe case had expired.
