OL,7,FHe expressed sympathy for the "human
OL,8,Fpain" of those who have lost their
OL,9,Fhomes.
OL,11,FAmid suggestions that the city centre
OL,12,Fdevelopment may have to be demolished,
OL,13,Fthe court heard some residents could
OL,14,Fnow face financial ruin.
OL,16,FCompleted back in 2008, the building
OL,17,Fon Chichester Street contains a total
OL,18,Fof 91 apartments.
