OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FBut in April 2019 all residents were
OL,8,Ftold to vacate their flats following
OL,9,Fan assessment of a structural column.
OL,11,FUlster Garden Villages Ltd, a charity
OL,12,Fwhich owns 54 of the apartments, and
OL,13,Fnearly 30 individual owners joined
OL,14,Fforces to sue the builders and
OL,15,Farchitects involved in the development.
OL,17,FThey claimed for structural defects,
OL,18,Fnegligence and loss of value in a
OL,19,Fjoint lawsuit estimated to be worth up
OL,20,Fto #25m.
