OL,7,FConstruction firms Farrans and Gilbert-
OL,8,FAsh, along with architecture company
OL,9,FBuilding Design Partnership, all
OL,10,Fvehemently denied any liability.
OL,12,FThe three defendants applied to have
OL,13,Fthe action struck out on the grounds
OL,14,Fthat it was statute barred.
OL,16,FUnder the terms of the Defective
OL,17,FPremises (NI) Order 1975 (DPO), a
OL,18,Fclaim for compensation had to be
OL,19,Flodged within six years of completing
OL,20,Fwork on the building.
