OL,7,FGranting the defendants' application,
OL,8,FMr Justice Huddleston held that it
OL,9,Fwould be unfair to allow the case
OL,10,Fagainst them to continue.
OL,12,F"I find against the plaintiffs, they
OL,13,Fare caught by the six year time
OL,14,Flimit," he confirmed.
OL,16,FThe judge also rejected the claims for
OL,17,Fnegligence, finding instead that the
OL,18,Fcase raised issues of "pure economic
OL,19,Floss".
