OL,7,FHe acknowledged "the personal trauma
OL,8,Fand worry" for owners of the
OL,9,Fapartments but stressed his decision
OL,10,Fwas based on policy considerations
OL,11,Fwithin the DPO.
OL,13,FUnder separate building safety
OL,14,Flegislation introduced in England and
OL,15,FWales in 2022 following the Grenfell
OL,16,FTower disaster, the limitation period
OL,17,Ffor enforcement of remedial work has
OL,18,Fbeen extended to 30 years.
